name: Lumo-8B-Instruct
description: Lumo Labs is a dynamic, open-source community at the forefront of innovation within the Solana ecosystem. They specialize in developing advanced AI models uniquely designed to enhance and expand Solana's capabilities. As the creators of the groundbreaking Lumo 70B and Lumo 8B models—the largest AI models ever built and trained on Solana—they leverage the unparalleled Lumo Iris Dataset, the most extensive training dataset in the Solana ecosystem, to power their advancements.
